'''托馬斯·麥克唐納'''（{{lang-en|'''Thomas McDonell'''}}，{{bd|1986年|5月2日}}）美國男演員及音樂人，在電影《[[功夫之王|功夫之王]]》中曾經與[[成龍|成龍]]及[[李連杰|李連杰]]有合作機會。托馬斯生於[[紐約|紐約]][[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]<ref name=ino>{{cite news | url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/04/22/PKD31J10CQ.DTL | work=The San Francisco Chronicle | first=Regan | last=McMahon | title='Prom' gears up for big night | date=12 May 2011 | accessdate=2020-10-11 | archive-date=2019-12-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215151631/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2011%2F04%2F22%2FPKD31J10CQ.DTL | dead-url=no }}</ref>，求學時被父母送往[[馬薩諸塞州|馬薩諸塞州]][[安多佛|安多佛]]的寄宿學校<ref>[http://www.miamiherald.com/2011/04/29/2190693/talking-to-the-stars-of-prom.html ]{{dead link|date=November 2011}}</ref>，及後於[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]畢業。他的父親{{link-en|特里·麥克唐納|Terry McDonell}}是雜誌《運動畫刊》的[[總編輯|總編輯]]<ref name=ino/><ref name=reb>{{Cite book|last=Johnson|first=Curt|authorlink=|coauthors=|title=Who's who in U.S. writers, editors & poets, Volume 1|publisher=December Press|year=1988|location=|pages=|month=|url=https://archive.org/details/whoswhoinuswrite0000unse|isbn=0-913204-21-8}}</ref>，母親及兄長（{{link-en|尼克·麥克唐納|Nick McDonell}}）都是作家<ref name=wylloh>{{cite web |last=Barker |first=Lynn |url=http://www.teenhollywood.com/2011/04/25/thomas-mcdonell-kind-of-prom |title=Thomas McDonell: King of "Prom" |publisher=TeenHollywood.com |date=2011-04-25 |accessdate=2011-11-26 |archive-date=2014-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020185458/http://www.teenhollywood.com/2011/04/25/thomas-mcdonell-kind-of-prom |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ethnicelebs.com/thomas-mcdonell |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-06-19 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116022855/https://ethnicelebs.com/thomas-mcdonell |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

